ygData.msgSnippet: Oh yes.  You should see what the bone chip and orc belt quests in Kaladim do now.  My Dwarf Paladin went from 4th to 7th in about 2 hours by just carting
ygData.messageBody:
Oh yes. You should see what the bone chip and orc belt quests in Kaladim do
now. My Dwarf Paladin went from 4th to 7th in about 2 hours by just carting
bone-chips and belts from Lesser Fay and Kelethin to Kaladim. And made a
profit! Not to mention being beloved by both the Paladin and warriors'
guilds now.

Kit

wow... did they up the exp on those small quests a lot or what?
I never got any exp from those when I was small, I got an item
like a rusty sword, or a spell, and sometimes a moonstone. Now
I hear you just get a moonstone.

Harmonic.
